title: U.S. launches probe into auto imports
text:
U.S. launches probe into auto imports Thursday, May 24, 2018 - 01:11
The U.S. Commerce Department said on Wednesday it will open a so-called Section 232 investigation into whether imports of vehicles and auto parts harm national security. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
